{"tid":591013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擔心華間諜活動 澳國防部員工禁用微信","createTime":"2018-03-13T07:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T07:11:07.000Z","uid":10958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e965c0f28e7e8d0c84c448220d90f372f4d4bd","tid":591013,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>擔心華間諜活動 澳國防部員工禁用微信</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kb2w.mWfoyyUiToEgvBfvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/13JHE001__20180313_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fkb2w.mWfoyyUiToEgvBfvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F13JHE001__20180313_L.jpg&h=135187ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">澳洲方面擔心微信的數據或被利用。（資料圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mJJMvGDft8tc4VJAznEZIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MjIzO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/018_01_a_20180313_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmJJMvGDft8tc4VJAznEZIg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MjIzO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F018_01_a_20180313_L.jpg&h=c4791909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【晴報專訊】澳洲傳媒報道，該國國防部已禁止員工在工作手機上，下載中國應用程序微信，這進一步凸顯澳擔心中國的「間諜活動」。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲金融評論報》前天引述國防部一名發言人稱，國防部不提供或支持在國防部的移動設備上，使用未經授權的軟件，包括微信。國防部只允許現役軍人有限使用facebook，對WhatsApp則正進行「安全評估」。<br />\n<br />\n一名據稱與澳洲聯邦政府有聯繫的網絡安全專家表示，對微信的擔心並非僅限於它與中國政府的密切關係，也與其用戶數據可能被「利用」有關，「他們（國防部）認為像微信這樣的應用軟件具有更高的收集和監控數據的能力」。<br />\n<br />\n藉國安反對中企投資<br />\n<br />\n報道又稱，與澳國防部有業務往來的企業尚未禁用微信，兩家專業服務企業表示，員工在與中國客戶打交道時經常使用微信。<br />\n<br />\n報道還認為，澳軍方禁用微信，是澳美等國以國家安全為由，反對中企投資的行為之一。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，在去年11月，印度國防部亦向沿中印實際控制綫駐紮士兵下達指令，要求他們刪除微信和微博。<br />\n<br />\n編輯：許何<br />\n<br />\n美術：熊偉然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E8%8F%AF%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E6%BE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1-224642760.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A6%2581%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1-224642760.html&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVH54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6d08bfd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E8%8F%AF%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E6%BE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1-224642760.html</a>"}]}